        <div class="article-title">Context Is Not a Trait. It's an Environment.</div>
        <div class="article-excerpt">Your audience isn't one person. They're the same person in ten different states. Stop building campaigns for who they are. Build them for the moment they're in — because that moment is the only thing you can actually influence.</div>
        <div class="article-tag">Context · Behavioral Strategy</div>
