        <div class="article-excerpt">Consistency is preached like gospel in brand strategy. But for brands trying to grow into new markets or audiences, rigid consistency can be the exact thing holding them back from behavioral relevance.</div>
        <div class="article-tag">Brand Strategy · Identity</div>
      </div>
