        <div class="article-excerpt">Personas flatten human behavior into fixed archetypes. Behavioral strategy asks a different question: what context activates this person to act — and how do we engineer that context into our campaigns?</div>
        <div class="article-tag">Segmentation · Behavioral Marketing</div>
      </div>
