        <div class="article-excerpt">Conventional wisdom says remove all friction from the customer journey. But strategic friction — placed deliberately — can increase commitment, reduce churn, and attract higher-quality customers. Know which kind you have.</div>
        <div class="article-tag">Friction · Conversion</div>
